{"title_page": "Bole, Xinjiang", "text_new": "{{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n|name                    = {{raise|0.2em|Bole}}\n|official_name           = <!-- Official name in English if different from 'name' -->\n|native_name             = {{lower|0.1em|{{lang|zh-hans|\u535a\u4e50\u5e02}}<br/>{{lang|ug-Arab|\u0628\u0648\u0631\u062a\u0627\u0644\u0627 \u0634\u06d5\u06be\u0649\u0631\u0649}}}}\n|other_name              = \n|settlement_type         = [[County-level city]]\n|pushpin_map             = China Xinjiang\n|pushpin_label_position  =\n|pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Xinjiang\n|pushpin_mapsize         =\n|coordinates             ={{coord|44.8539|N|82.0514|E|type:adm3rd_region:CN-65_source:Gaode|format=dms|display=it}}\n|coor_pinpoint = Bole municipal government\n|image_skyline           = In Lake Sayram Scenic Spot, Xinjiang, China 50.jpg\n|imagesize               = \n|image_alt               = \n|image_caption           = Sayram Lake\n|flag_alt                = \n|image_seal              = \n|seal_size               = \n|seal_alt                = \n|image_shield            = \n|shield_size             = \n|shield_alt              = \n|image_blank_emblem      = \n|blank_emblem_type       = \n|blank_emblem_size       = \n|blank_emblem_alt        = \n|nickname                = \n|motto                   = \n|image_map               = \n|mapsize                 = \n|map_alt                 = \n|map_caption             = \n|image_map1              = \n|mapsize1                = \n|map_alt1                = \n|map_caption1            = \n|image_dot_map           = \n|dot_mapsize             = \n|dot_map_base_alt        = \n|dot_map_alt             = \n|dot_map_caption         = \n|dot_x = |dot_y =\n|coordinates_footnotes   = \n|subdivision_type        = Country\n|subdivision_name        = [[China|People's Republic of China]]\n|subdivision_type1       = [[Autonomous regions of China|Autonomous region]]\n|subdivision_name1       = [[Xinjiang]]\n|subdivision_type2       = [[Autonomous prefecture]]\n|subdivision_name2       = [[Bortala Mongol Autonomous Prefecture|Bortala (Mongol)]]\n|established_title       = \n|established_date        = \n|founder                 = \n|named_for               = \n|seat_type               = \n|seat                    = \n|government_footnotes    = \n|government_type         = \n|leader_party            = \n|leader_title            = \n|leader_name             = \n|leader_title1           = \n|leader_name1            = \n|total_type              = \n|unit_pref               = \n|area_magnitude          = \n|area_footnotes          = \n|area_total_km2          = 7801.68\n|area_land_km2           = \n|area_water_km2          = \n|area_water_percent      = \n|elevation_footnotes     = \n|elevation_m             = 662\n|elevation_ft            = \n|population_footnotes    = \n|population_total        = 106400\n|population_as_of        = 2011\n|population_density_km2  = auto\n|population_est           = \n|pop_est_as_of            = \n|population_note          = \n|postal_code_type = [[Postal code of China|Postal code]]\n|postal_code              = 833400\n|area_code_type           = \n|area_code                = 909\n|registration_plate       = {{lang|zh-cn|\u65b0E}}\n|website                  = {{URL|www.xjboz.gov.cn/}}\n|footnotes                = \n}}\n{{Infobox Chinese\n|s=\u535a\u4e50\n|t=\u535a\u6a02\n|p=B\u00f3l\u00e8\n|s2=\u535a\u5c14\u5854\u62c9\n|t2=\u535a\u723e\u5854\u62c9\n|p2=B\u00f3'\u011brt\u01cel\u0101\n|mong=\u182a\u1823\u1837\u1823\u1832\u1820\u182f\u180e\u1820\n|uig=\u0628\u06c6\u0631\u062a\u0627\u0644\u0627\n|uly=B\u00f6rtala\n|uyy=B\u0275rtala\n|sgs=Bortala\n|usy=\u0411\u04e9\u0440\u0442\u0430\u043b\u0430\n|order=st\n}}\n'''Bole''' as the official romanized name, also [[SASM/GNC romanization|transliterated from Mongolian]] as '''Bortala''', is a [[county-level city]] in [[Xinjiang]], China. The city covers an area of {{convert|7517|km2}} and {{as of|2003|lc=y}} had a total population of 403,700 (2003). Bortala means \"brown grasslands/steppe\" in [[Mongolian language|Mongolian]]. Bortala is the seat of [[Bortala Mongol Autonomous Prefecture]], which borders [[Kazakhstan]]. The [[Northern Xinjiang Railway]] runs through the city along with highways to [[\u00dcr\u00fcmqi]].\n\n==Geography==\n{{Weather box\n|location = Bole, Xinjiang (1981\u20132010 normals)\n|metric first = Y\n|single line  = Y\n|Jan high C = \u22129.6\n|Feb high C = \u22125.4\n|Mar high C =  5.2\n|Apr high C = 17.9\n|May high C = 25.1\n|Jun high C = 30.0\n|Jul high C = 31.7\n|Aug high C = 30.2\n|Sep high C = 23.9\n|Oct high C = 14.6\n|Nov high C =  3.1\n|Dec high C = \u22126.7\n\n|Jan mean C = \u221215.7\n|Feb mean C = \u221211.5\n|Mar mean C =  \u22120.1\n|Apr mean C =  11.1\n|May mean C =  17.8\n|Jun mean C =  22.3\n|Jul mean C =  23.8\n|Aug mean C =  22.2\n|Sep mean C =  16.5\n|Oct mean C =   8.0\n|Nov mean C =  \u22121.5\n|Dec mean C = \u221211.4\n\n|Jan low C = \u221220.5\n|Feb low C = \u221216.7\n|Mar low C =  \u22124.8\n|Apr low C =   4.9\n|May low C =  11.1\n|Jun low C =  15.1\n|Jul low C =  16.5\n|Aug low C =  14.9\n|Sep low C =   9.6\n|Oct low C =   2.6\n|Nov low C =  -5.0\n|Dec low C = \u221215.1\n|precipitation colour = green\n|Jan precipitation mm =  5.3\n|Feb precipitation mm =  6.8\n|Mar precipitation mm =  8.9\n|Apr precipitation mm = 19.4\n|May precipitation mm = 32.3\n|Jun precipitation mm = 28.9\n|Jul precipitation mm = 29.1\n|Aug precipitation mm = 18.7\n|Sep precipitation mm = 17.9\n|Oct precipitation mm = 15.5\n|Nov precipitation mm =  8.5\n|Dec precipitation mm =  8.9\n|Jan humidity = 81\n|Feb humidity = 80\n|Mar humidity = 73\n|Apr humidity = 55\n|May humidity = 52\n|Jun humidity = 52\n|Jul humidity = 56\n|Aug humidity = 56\n|Sep humidity = 59\n|Oct humidity = 67\n|Nov humidity = 79\n|Dec humidity = 83\n|source 1 = China Meteorological Admini